### Регистрация
POST http://localhost:5141/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### Логин
POST http://localhost:5141/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### Добавить с тегами и новыми полями
POST http://localhost:5141/api/JobApplications
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..hL18eEdbQYgKafoZbBHoS9m8KMihErnfpAxPA_MemeU
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "companyName": "Noir",
    "position": ".NET Developer",
    "status": "Pending",
    "appliedDate": "2026-06-19T00:00:00",
    "salaryMin": 75000,
    "salaryMax": 95000,
    "location": "London, Remote",
    "tags": [".NET", "Azure", "C#"]
}

### Парсинг вакансии
POST http://localhost:5141/api/JobApplications/parse
Authorization: Bearer <твой токен>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "jobText": "About the job\n\n.NET Developer - Global Sports Company – London\n\n(Tech stack: .NET Developer, .NET 10.0, ASP.NET Core, C# 14, .NET Aspire, CI/CD, Azure DevOps, EF Core 10.0)\n\nOur client is a global sports brand... Salary: £75,000 - £95,000 + Bonus + Pension + Benefits\n\nLocation: London, UK / Remote Working"
}